# Monorepo core

Read `AGENTS.md` first.

## Scope (hard)

Declare Goal / In scope / Out of scope / Owner / Tier before edits.

| Tier | Max files | Packages |
|------|-----------|----------|
| XS | 2 | 1 |
| S | 5 | 1 |
| M | 10 | ≤2 + plan |
| L | >10 | plan + user OK |

Exceeded → stop, report, ask to split.

Default **out of scope:** `packages/ui/**`, `apps/api/**`, `apps/mock-server/**`.

## Verification gates (required)

```bash
npm run build -w @all-according-to-plan/shared -w @all-according-to-plan/game-engine
```

If `apps/web` touched: `cd apps/web && npm run build && npm run lint`

Full monorepo if workspace deps changed: `npm run build && npm run lint`

Engine logic change without tests: include Gate D manual checklist in report.

## Forbidden (no explicit user approval)

- git commit/push/PR
- New npm dependencies
- `Math.random()` outside `game-engine/src/rng.ts`
- Direct `GameState` mutation in UI
- Repo-wide format/lint
- Deleting `public/audio` or `public/cards`

## Style

Single quotes · minimal comments · smallest diff
